l seven known Trombicula s. s. species is provided. The differentiation of Trombicula s. s. group is based on leg segmentation fsp\u2009=\u20096.6.6, rugose scutum with complete AM, AL and PL setation, and fT\u2009=\u20095B, 5BN or 4B2N.\nConclusion\u2002 A new species within the genus Trombicula, group minor has been described. The new species also increases the number of known chiggers in Indonesia and the number of species parasitizing the host species Hipposideros diadema. Trombicula s. s. has also been revised and more clearly defined.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Kal\u00faz, Stanislav", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "\u0160r\u00e1mek, Petr", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "\u0160ev\u010d\u00edk, Martin", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/463e80171814af7a2580f3d66ab03754", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/6418caf8064c4171287b1fb77109bebe52501d0d858b0cc7f06b91dc1661c3f3", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/YA4E6Z33", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/YA4E6Z33", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/fb881b9d58c1c5e4a22b48205dd84fd8!/b56947-59408", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "1", "pages": "865-873", "title": 